<i>They are trying to hide behind</i>
<i>frills and wedding bouquets.</i>

11:56.016 --> 11:58.450
<i>We must arm ourselves,</i>
<i>america --</i>

11:58.452 --> 12:01.186
<i>Not with guns</i>
<i>but with the truth.</i>

12:06.026 --> 12:07.358
Say something.
Don't just stare.

12:07.360 --> 12:09.260
I'm still processing the fact
that you did this.

12:09.262 --> 12:12.997
You're still -- excuse me?

12:12.999 --> 12:14.733
Casting your lot
with olivia pope,

12:14.735 --> 12:17.035
Backing this terrible idea,
without checking with me,

12:17.037 --> 12:19.337
Your campaign manager?
What in the hell was that?

12:21.441 --> 12:23.942
We are not partners.
We are not friends.

12:23.944 --> 12:25.877
You work for me.
You fix for me.

12:25.879 --> 12:28.046
You don't accuse me.
You do not judge me.

12:28.048 --> 12:30.215
You most certainly do not
lecture me.

12:30.217 --> 12:32.067
You are<i> not</i> me.

12:32.068 --> 12:33.918
You wish you were me,
but you can't be me.

12:33.920 --> 12:35.453
Remind yourself of that.

12:35.455 --> 12:37.188
Do you understand?

12:37.190 --> 12:38.323
I wasn't implying --

12:38.325 --> 12:39.958
I have a position.
You have a job.

12:39.960 --> 12:41.826
You fix.
That's your job.

12:41.828 --> 12:42.961
You fix or you leave.

12:42.963 --> 12:44.062
Do you have a problem
with that?

12:44.064 --> 12:45.964
No, i --
because if you do...

12:45.966 --> 12:47.031
I do not.

12:47.033 --> 12:48.032
Are you sure?

12:48.034 --> 12:50.935
I am quite sure,
mrs. Grant.

12:50.937 --> 12:52.237
Why don't i start by helping
michael's parents

12:52.239 --> 12:53.271
Get here for the wedding?

12:53.273 --> 12:54.973
Why don't you do that?

12:54.975 --> 12:58.877
I'm on it.
Thank you, mrs. Grant.

13:02.182 --> 13:04.115
No one's going
to take this seriously.

13:04.117 --> 13:06.451
She's a grown woman who thinks
angels are real.

13:06.453 --> 13:08.670
Don't underestimate her.

13:08.671 --> 13:10.888
Sally langston has an audience
of 3.8 million devoted fans.

13:10.891 --> 13:12.924
And she's offering
cash money.

13:12.926 --> 13:14.359
She's not gonna find
anything.

13:14.361 --> 13:15.961
Michael,
i need you to think back

13:15.962 --> 13:17.562
On anything you may have said
or done over the past few months

13:17.564 --> 13:20.965
That could be construed
as inappropriate.

13:20.967 --> 13:22.901
Sally langston is a dog
who won't stop digging

13:22.903 --> 13:26.070
Until she's sure
there aren't any bones
buried in your backyard.

13:26.072 --> 13:27.939
Like i said, i'm clean.

13:32.145 --> 13:33.528
Huck, look into michael.

13:33.529 --> 13:34.912
See if he's been sleeping
with anyone

13:34.915 --> 13:36.281
Since he and cyrus
moved in together.

13:36.283 --> 13:37.816
You think he's lying?

13:37.817 --> 13:39.350
I think if he's lying,
we need to be prepared.

13:39.351 --> 13:40.884
I want to know where
sally langston's
getting her intel.

13:40.887 --> 13:42.120
It's too accurate.
She knows about the marriage.

13:42.122 --> 13:44.072
She knows about
white house meetings.

13:44.073 --> 13:46.023
Someone's leaking to her --
somebody inside the white house.

13:46.026 --> 13:48.092
Who in the white house
would give info to sally?

13:49.062 --> 13:52.030
Somebody who doesn't know
they're giving info to sally.

13:52.032 --> 13:53.031
Leave without me.

13:55.468 --> 13:57.068
Abby: You played me!

13:57.070 --> 13:58.536
What are you talking about?

13:58.538 --> 14:00.772
I mentioned our war room
in passing,

14:00.774 --> 14:02.140
And you told sally langston.

14:02.142 --> 14:04.042
You're working for her!

14:04.044 --> 14:05.977
What did you
expect me to do?

14:05.979 --> 14:07.245
[ laughs ]

14:07.247 --> 14:08.346
[ gasps ]
unbelievable!

14:08.348 --> 14:09.981
Just admit that wedding
is a sham!

14:09.983 --> 14:12.317
Church and state, leo!
Church and state!

14:12.319 --> 14:13.852
I did church and state!

14:13.854 --> 14:15.019
You're the one
who told me things

14:15.021 --> 14:16.020
You should not
have told me.

14:16.022 --> 14:17.722
You're like the politicians

14:17.723 --> 14:19.423
Who claim they believe in the
separation of church and state

14:19.426 --> 14:21.960
But still voted to put the words
"one nation under god"

14:21.962 --> 14:23.561
In the pledge of allegiance
in the 1950s.

14:23.563 --> 14:26.264
You don't really believe.
You just say you do.

14:26.266 --> 14:29.000
You broke the barrier.
You talked. Not me.

14:29.002 --> 14:31.536
Don't you dare call me
a hypocritical secularist.

14:31.538 --> 14:33.037
Well, if the school
prayer fits.

14:33.039 --> 14:35.039
Leo!
You talked!

14:35.041 --> 14:37.408
You poked the hole
in the condom, not me.

14:37.410 --> 14:38.943
I kept it all wrapped up.

14:38.945 --> 14:40.578
I talked. Fine.

14:40.579 --> 14:42.212
But you didn't have to use
the information.

14:42.215 --> 14:43.481
Really?
[ keys thud ]

14:43.483 --> 14:46.184
Would you not have used
the information?

14:46.186 --> 14:48.586
Can you tell me
with absolute honesty

14:48.588 --> 14:51.990
You would never use any
information you learned from me?

14:51.992 --> 14:54.225
Think about that.

14:56.029 --> 14:58.930
You hypocritical
secularist!

14:58.932 --> 15:00.398
Church and state!

15:00.400 --> 15:02.000
[ door slams ]

15:14.915 --> 15:17.081
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

15:21.922 --> 15:23.655
What do you think
you're doing?

15:25.425 --> 15:26.958
Hello!

15:26.960 --> 15:30.194
I told you i don't want you
in here.

15:30.196 --> 15:34.065
You need to stay on your side
of my house!

15:35.435 --> 15:37.969
I know you can hear me,
you repulsive...

15:39.239 --> 15:41.072
Janet?

15:41.074 --> 15:43.341
We won! [ laughs ]

15:43.343 --> 15:45.443
Did you see the news?

15:45.445 --> 15:47.445
[ chuckles ]
i wish you'd been there.

15:47.447 --> 15:49.280
Election night,
governor grant --

15:49.282 --> 15:51.215
We took california
by storm, janet.

15:51.217 --> 15:53.952
We won.

15:53.954 --> 15:55.954
Look, i-i know
i-i-i've been absent

15:55.956 --> 15:57.422
These past couple
of months.

15:57.424 --> 15:58.974
[ sighs ]

15:58.975 --> 16:00.525
Fitz's campaign has been hell
for me.

16:00.527 --> 16:03.194
But it's over now.
We won!

16:03.196 --> 16:04.195
We should be celebrating.

16:04.197 --> 16:07.098
Celebrating. Right.

16:07.100 --> 16:09.334
Cheers, baby.

16:13.707 --> 16:16.007
What has gotten into you?

16:16.009 --> 16:19.610
My mother was a model,
cyrus.

16:19.612 --> 16:24.649
I was just so happy that a man
looked at me

16:24.651 --> 16:25.984
When you proposed.

16:25.986 --> 16:28.519
I didn't even know.

16:28.521 --> 16:32.490
And i definitely never knew
it could be different.

16:32.492 --> 16:34.492
I never knew
it<i> should</i> be different.

16:34.494 --> 16:38.496
But now it's different.
Now i know.

16:38.498 --> 16:40.064
And i thought
that getting drunk

16:40.066 --> 16:42.033
Would make
this conversation easier.

16:42.035 --> 16:44.068
I thought
it would make me brave.

16:44.070 --> 16:47.038
But now i'm just --
i'm just drunk and scared,

16:47.040 --> 16:48.039
So i w-want...

16:48.041 --> 16:50.008
A divorce, cyrus.

16:51.177 --> 16:53.044
You don't believe
in divorce.

16:53.046 --> 16:55.713
When i proposed,
you said you don't believe --

16:55.715 --> 16:59.183
I'm lonely here, cy --
<i>with</i> you.

16:59.185 --> 17:03.755
It has been 16 years,
and i barely know you.

17:03.757 --> 17:06.724
Being with you
is a lonely experience.

17:06.726 --> 17:09.027
No, no! You can't!

17:09.029 --> 17:10.595
[ breathing heavily ]

17:10.597 --> 17:14.265
Look, don't do this to me,
janet. Don't.

17:14.267 --> 17:17.535
Don't leave me --
not right now,

17:17.537 --> 17:18.736
Not when it's about
to be my turn.

17:18.738 --> 17:21.105
[ laughing ] your turn?

17:21.107 --> 17:22.473
I'm making a run
for congress --

17:22.475 --> 17:24.342
With fitz's connections,
and with you...

17:24.344 --> 17:26.277
Janet.

17:26.279 --> 17:27.812
I can make this happen.

17:27.814 --> 17:29.480
We won
comptroller together.

17:29.482 --> 17:30.748
We can win this one, too --

17:30.750 --> 17:32.150
With you by my side.

17:32.152 --> 17:35.119
I can be congressman --
if i have a wife!

17:35.121 --> 17:38.089
At the very least,

17:38.091 --> 17:40.758
Let's stop pretending
with one another.

17:40.760 --> 17:45.296
How about i will admit
that i'm not having an affair

17:45.298 --> 17:48.800
If you'll admit
you aren't gay?

17:59.679 --> 18:01.813
Goodbye, cyrus.

18:01.815 --> 18:03.548
[ breathing heavily ]

18:09.522 --> 18:11.522
James: Cyrus.

18:11.524 --> 18:14.092
Cyrus? Are you okay?

18:14.094 --> 18:17.695
Because if this is happening
too fast, just tell me.

18:18.631 --> 18:20.164
Michael:
There was a laundry mix-up.

18:20.166 --> 18:22.567
A couple of my shirts ended up
in your closet.

18:22.569 --> 18:25.103
Don't worry, i'll stick
to my side of your house.

18:29.642 --> 18:31.809
Turns out,
michael has a second phone.

18:31.811 --> 18:33.111
It only gets calls
from one number --

18:33.113 --> 18:34.746
A guy called phillip reed.

18:34.747 --> 18:36.380
<i>I had an amazing time</i>
<i>last night, michael.</i>

18:36.382 --> 18:37.715
<i>I've been thinking about you</i>

18:37.717 --> 18:39.650
<i>Pinning me up against the wall</i>
<i>and shoving --</i>

18:39.652 --> 18:41.652
So michael lied.
It's worse than that.

18:41.654 --> 18:43.438
Turns out that --
sally langston

18:43.439 --> 18:45.223
Has got some guy named
phillip reed booked
on her next show.

18:45.225 --> 18:46.491
I think he's gonna say
he's --

18:46.493 --> 18:48.143
Having an affair
with michael.

18:48.144 --> 18:49.794
How did you know?
I pulled
michael's cell records,

18:49.796 --> 18:51.429
Did a search
for most-called numbers,

18:51.431 --> 18:52.797
Came up with phillip,
triangulated cellphone towers

18:52.799 --> 18:54.532
To track him to the vicinity
of his office server,

18:54.534 --> 18:56.501
And then i hacked
into their e-mail system.
How'd you find out?

18:56.503 --> 18:57.835
I listened to all of

18:57.837 --> 18:59.203
Leo's voice-mails
when he was in the bathroom.

18:59.205 --> 19:00.905
Well,
that's another way to go.

19:00.907 --> 19:03.091
Let's go.

19:03.092 --> 19:05.276
Man:
<i>This sunday, sally langston's</i>
<i>exclusive interview</i>

19:05.278 --> 19:07.845
<i>Blows the lid off</i>
<i>cyrus beene's sham wedding.</i>

19:07.847 --> 19:10.181
<i>Let freedom ring.</i>

19:10.183 --> 19:12.717
<i>The liberty report --</i>
<i>sunday at 8:00.</i>

19:12.719 --> 19:15.253
So, apparently, michael's
been seeing this guy

19:15.255 --> 19:17.221
On and off
for seven months.

19:17.223 --> 19:18.823
So he lied.
He lied.

19:18.825 --> 19:19.891
That's what he does best.

19:19.893 --> 19:21.459
Then we need to cancel
the wedding.

19:21.461 --> 19:22.727
Abby: Oh, we can't cancel
the wedding.

19:22.729 --> 19:23.661
The optics of that alone...

19:23.663 --> 19:25.029
Everything's already booked.

19:25.030 --> 19:26.396
It'd be a public-relations
nightmare.

19:26.397 --> 19:27.763
It already<i> is</i>
a public-relations nightmare.

19:27.767 --> 19:30.268
This guy is set to appear
on sally's show on sunday.

19:30.270 --> 19:32.403
I agree. Call it off.
I'm sorry, cyrus.

19:32.405 --> 19:34.572
No one is calling anything off.
No one is quitting --

19:34.574 --> 19:36.507
Not until i've tried
everything -- everything!

19:36.509 --> 19:38.276
Is that clear?

19:41.814 --> 19:43.714
Okay, then.

19:45.585 --> 19:47.351
[ door opens ]

19:47.353 --> 19:48.953
[ door closes ]
"okay, then."

19:48.955 --> 19:50.188
[ scoffs ]

19:54.294 --> 19:56.227
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

20:03.836 --> 20:05.903
[ sighs ]

20:11.678 --> 20:15.279
He's the one who wanted this --
vermont, the inn,

20:15.281 --> 20:17.748
The little milk pails full
of flowers on the tables.

20:17.750 --> 20:19.317
All james --
not cyrus, james.

20:19.319 --> 20:21.352
And now the president
of the united states

20:21.354 --> 20:23.888
Is gonna be looking on as i get
stood up at the altar.

20:23.890 --> 20:24.989
Goody.

20:24.991 --> 20:27.425
Cyrus, talk to him.

20:36.903 --> 20:38.770
Did olivia tell you
to come here?

20:38.771 --> 20:40.638
She says you're worried i'm
going to ruin your career.

20:40.640 --> 20:42.306
"cripple your journalistic
integrity,"

20:42.308 --> 20:43.841
I believe were
the words she used.

20:43.843 --> 20:46.677
I didn't tell her that,
but she's right.

20:46.679 --> 20:48.913
I want to be
cyrus beene's husband,

20:48.915 --> 20:50.715
And i want
to be a journalist,

20:50.717 --> 20:52.917
But i don't want to be
"cyrus beene's husband,

20:52.919 --> 20:54.252
The journalist."

20:54.254 --> 20:56.070
I want to be married
to you,

20:56.071 --> 20:57.887
But i don't want anyone to think
that i'm your lapdog.

20:57.890 --> 20:59.690
Does that make sense?
Of course it does.

20:59.692 --> 21:01.792
I'm never gonna ask you
to do that --

21:01.794 --> 21:04.729
Compromise your principles,
influence your work.

21:04.731 --> 21:05.963
I love you
too much for that.

21:05.965 --> 21:07.531
Do you promise?

21:07.533 --> 21:09.834
I promise.

21:09.836 --> 21:11.586
[ chuckles ]

21:11.587 --> 21:13.337
You know, you're pretty hot
when you get all sincere.

21:13.339 --> 21:15.940
So for the love of god...

21:15.942 --> 21:17.708
[ sighs ]

21:17.710 --> 21:19.844
...Won't you come inside
and marry me?

21:35.795 --> 21:37.928
[<i> camera shutter clicking</i> ]

21:53.680 --> 21:54.945
[ gasps ]

21:54.947 --> 21:56.681
[ breathing heavily ]

22:01.921 --> 22:04.322
Fitz:
Don't you love vermont?

22:04.324 --> 22:08.426
Where's the rest
of your suit?

22:08.428 --> 22:09.860
Would you believe
senator martinez

22:09.862 --> 22:11.495
Spilled
a cape codder on it?

22:11.497 --> 22:13.631
They're bringing me
a new one.

22:13.633 --> 22:16.634
I never saw cyrus as much
of a rose-petal guy.

22:16.636 --> 22:19.437
On his wedding day,
he's a rose-petal guy.

22:21.974 --> 22:23.774
No.

22:23.776 --> 22:25.876
Open the door.

22:25.878 --> 22:27.878
I just want to know what i did
wrong, why you left.

22:27.880 --> 22:29.580
This is cyrus' day.
Don't do this.

22:29.582 --> 22:30.965
Why you resigned.

22:30.966 --> 22:32.349
I wouldn't have come if i
thought you were going --

22:32.352 --> 22:33.918
Even if you didn't want to be
with me,

22:33.920 --> 22:35.853
I don't understand why you would
leave the white house.

22:35.855 --> 22:37.621
You<i> are</i> the white house!

22:37.623 --> 22:39.023
I don't want to be there.

22:39.025 --> 22:41.859
I can't be there
and see you every day.

22:47.400 --> 22:49.900
Well...

22:49.902 --> 22:51.569
I asked.

23:01.881 --> 23:03.414
It's a ring --

23:03.416 --> 23:07.918
Very old, rare,
one of a kind.

23:07.920 --> 23:10.054
It even has a name --
doux bebe.

23:10.056 --> 23:12.490
It was my
great-grandmother's.

23:12.492 --> 23:15.793
Her father bought it for her
at auction in paris.

23:15.795 --> 23:18.629
She wore it
at her debutante ball.

23:18.631 --> 23:22.933
And i was supposed to give it
to my wife, but i didn't.

23:22.935 --> 23:25.703
It just...

23:25.705 --> 23:26.904
Never felt right.

23:26.906 --> 23:29.106
So i kept it.

23:29.108 --> 23:32.910
And now i know why --

23:32.912 --> 23:35.780
Because i was supposed
to give it to you.

23:43.956 --> 23:46.624
I don't want a ring
from you.

23:46.626 --> 23:48.959
Don't think of it as a ring.

23:48.961 --> 23:50.995
Don't think of it as...

23:53.900 --> 23:55.633
You don't have to love me.

23:55.635 --> 23:56.967
[ scoffs, sniffles ]

23:56.969 --> 23:59.437
You don't have to
come back to me.

23:59.439 --> 24:03.474
But if you could wear this,

24:03.476 --> 24:06.110
If i could know that you
were wearing this,

24:06.112 --> 24:10.214
Then even if you hate me,
i'll know...

24:10.216 --> 24:11.882
We'll be okay.

24:11.884 --> 24:13.217
I'll know you're out there.

24:18.891 --> 24:20.758
[ breathes deeply ]

24:27.967 --> 24:29.567
[ sniffles ]

24:33.573 --> 24:35.039
[ fitz sighs ]

24:44.951 --> 24:46.917
Doux bebe?
That's its name?

24:46.919 --> 24:48.552
[ both chuckle ]

24:48.553 --> 24:50.186
You can call it
whatever you want.

24:50.187 --> 24:51.820
In english, doux bebe means
"sweet baby," so...

24:51.824 --> 24:53.991
You want me to call a ring
"sweet baby"? [ chuckles ]

24:53.993 --> 24:57.061
I just want you
to be happy.

25:00.266 --> 25:01.565
[ exhales sharply ]

25:04.637 --> 25:05.636
[ sniffles ]

25:18.851 --> 25:21.552
I could never hate you.

25:26.692 --> 25:27.925
[ crying ]

25:34.000 --> 25:35.733
[ sniffles, sighs ]

25:35.735 --> 25:37.868
I should...

25:37.870 --> 25:39.169
[ sighs ]

25:43.109 --> 25:44.074
[ breathing heavily ]

25:58.558 --> 25:59.256
[ gasps ]

25:59.258 --> 26:01.292
[ ring jingling ]

26:11.637 --> 26:13.637
[ door opens ]

26:16.108 --> 26:18.642
[ door closes ]

26:20.846 --> 26:23.047
Liv.

26:25.851 --> 26:29.887
I need to ask you for something
for cyrus.

26:29.889 --> 26:31.589
Anything.

26:31.591 --> 26:34.158
Don't say that
till you've seen it.

26:40.032 --> 26:43.334
Sally langston -- we're gonna
need a bargaining chip.

27:04.890 --> 27:08.826
You went around my back
to mellie.

27:12.698 --> 27:15.032
I did.

27:15.034 --> 27:17.334
Nice move.

27:30.182 --> 27:32.049
Mrs. Vice president.
Thank you for seeing me.

27:32.051 --> 27:33.350
No need to be so formal,
ms. Pope.

27:33.352 --> 27:35.803
It's just plain,
old "sally" now.

27:35.804 --> 27:38.255
I'd like to talk to you
about sunday's guest.
Phillip reed,

27:38.257 --> 27:39.957
The piece of fluff
who proves

27:39.959 --> 27:41.792
That cyrus beene's
living arrangement

27:41.794 --> 27:43.794
Is as bogus and empty
as the man himself?

27:43.796 --> 27:45.362
You're not on camera,
sally.

27:45.363 --> 27:46.929
Hyperion is calling about
a book deal in five minutes.

27:46.932 --> 27:48.799
You should use this time
wisely, ms. Pope.

27:48.801 --> 27:51.735
You know what i do,
so what do you want?

27:51.737 --> 27:54.238
Because this --
this can't be it.

27:54.240 --> 27:56.006
You were almost the president
of this country,

27:56.008 --> 27:57.675
And now you're signing up
with the weekly gasbags?

27:57.677 --> 27:59.043
It doesn't make sense.
I take offense to that,

27:59.045 --> 28:00.944
Especially
coming from a woman

28:00.946 --> 28:03.747
Who's nothing but a shill
for defilers and fornicators.

28:03.749 --> 28:05.399
During the election,

28:05.400 --> 28:07.050
