you demolished him.

28:08.888 --> 28:10.371
In fact, the only area

28:10.372 --> 28:11.855
He polled ahead of you
was foreign policy.

28:11.857 --> 28:13.691
Was it sexism?
Probably.

28:13.693 --> 28:14.858
But that's nothing
a couple years

28:14.860 --> 28:15.993
As secretary of state
can't fix.

28:15.995 --> 28:17.161
[ scoffs ]
secretary of state?

28:17.163 --> 28:18.796
