that do not involve

28:58.804 --> 29:01.071
The three square miles
around the washington mall.

29:02.475 --> 29:04.007
Right there --

29:04.009 --> 29:05.909
That is the real seat
of power.

29:05.911 --> 29:08.512
I'm exactly
where i need to be,

29:08.514 --> 29:11.115
