with his parents --

29:58.931 --> 30:01.031
Leak the location.
Seat us near a window.

30:01.033 --> 30:03.066
Make sure there are pics
and press.

30:03.068 --> 30:04.902
It'll make me
even more sympathetic

30:04.904 --> 30:06.570
When my heart is broken.

30:06.571 --> 30:08.237
Oh, liv, this is good.
This is very, very good.

30:08.240 --> 30:09.873
But to be clear,

30:09.875 --> 30:12.009
