high-school football.
Mm.

30:36.068 --> 30:37.501
For how long, dad,
35 years?

30:37.503 --> 30:40.037
11 state championships.
He sent two of his kids pro.

30:40.039 --> 30:41.472
Three.

30:41.473 --> 30:42.906
