paying us enough

31:00.359 --> 31:02.192
To have our picture taken
with you two

31:02.194 --> 31:03.560
Like we're okay with this.

31:03.562 --> 31:06.296
They're not paying you?
Who -- someone's paying you?

31:06.298 --> 31:07.965
Who's paying you?

31:07.967 --> 31:10.033
That woman --
pretty, godless.

31:10.035 --> 31:13.470
Elizabeth something.
Elizabeth north.

31:13.472 --> 31:15.639
Why else do you think
we're here?

31:15.641 --> 31:19.009
You think we approve of this --
of you, of what you are?

31:19.011 --> 31:22.012
You think we spent all that
money sending you to those camps

31:22.014 --> 31:24.381
To fix you, only to have you
end up like this?

31:24.383 --> 31:27.551
Oh, you make me sick
to my stomach, both of you.

31:37.463 --> 31:40.163
Put the food in your mouth.

31:41.934 --> 31:44.534
Isn't this something,
