of the united states

32:55.207 --> 32:58.008
In a pair of flip-flops
and a tommy bahama t-shirt.

32:58.010 --> 33:00.410
You're not going to st. Barts
to represent the white house.

33:00.412 --> 33:03.080
You are going there to enjoy
your honeymoon --<i> our</i> honeymoon.

33:03.082 --> 33:04.448
No tie, cy.
[ cellphone chimes ]

33:04.450 --> 33:07.250
[ groans ]
thank you.

33:07.252 --> 33:08.552
