down herself, but [sighs]

33:26.472 --> 33:30.140
Oh, cyrus,
you promised -- no work.

33:30.142 --> 33:32.142
Maybe you can shut it down.

33:32.144 --> 33:34.044
What?

33:34.046 --> 33:38.582
I probably shouldn't be
telling you this, but...

33:38.584 --> 33:39.750
[ sighs ]

33:39.752 --> 33:41.618
For months, the president

33:41.620 --> 33:44.087
