backroom deals

33:44.089 --> 33:47.290
In order to present an
immigration bill to congress

33:47.292 --> 33:49.659
That won't peter out
due to partisan politics.

33:49.661 --> 33:52.295
He wants to craft legislation
that can actually pass

33:52.297 --> 33:54.498
So that he can actually make
a difference.

33:54.500 --> 33:55.732
But if this story runs,

33:55.734 --> 33:57.801
If one of the most respected
newspapers

33:57.803 --> 34:00.137
In the country calls him out
on this...
[ sighs ]

34:00.139 --> 34:02.539
...He'll be forced
to push through

34:02.541 --> 34:05.208
Some half-assed bill
just to save face.

34:05.210 --> 34:07.310
He'll lose his political clout
on the hill,

34:07.312 --> 34:09.546
And all that back-scratching
and horse trading

34:09.548 --> 34:11.214
Will go straight out
the window.

34:11.216 --> 34:13.050
Immigration will be dead.

34:13.052 --> 34:14.518
[ sighs ]

34:14.520 --> 34:19.056
And w-who knows what else
will be killed in its path?

34:19.058 --> 34:21.558
I-i-i want us

34:21.560 --> 34:23.193
To have an amazing time
on our honeymoon.

34:23.195 --> 34:24.327
I really do.

34:24.329 --> 34:25.695
But if this story
comes out...

34:25.697 --> 34:28.665
Then our honeymoon will be over
before it began.

34:28.667 --> 34:30.567
[ both sigh ]

34:30.569 --> 34:33.170
I'm sorry, honey.
No.

34:33.172 --> 34:35.138
It's fine.

34:35.140 --> 34:37.240
I -- i-i'll --
i'll see what i can do.

