35:57.756 --> 35:58.822
I just need a minute.

35:58.824 --> 36:00.557
Jackie, if it's more
than a minute,

36:00.559 --> 36:01.892
Would you please
call security?

36:01.894 --> 36:03.777
[ chuckles ]

36:03.778 --> 36:05.661
